          provide lending solutions designed by pilots, for pilots. Secure the
          funding required for our 8-to-10 month fast-track with a partner that
          understands the true value of your flight deck seat.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-block bg-monza-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-monza-700 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl text-center"
          >
            Apply for Financing
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-block bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors border-2 border-white/20 text-center"
          >
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Finance Your Training -->
